videos.description: Tennessee's Evina Westbrook sets up Mercedes Russell down low for the layup in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Westbrook's crafty pass sets up Russell's lay-in

videos.description: Tennessee's Meme Jackson zips a pass upcourt to Mercedes Russell for the lay-in in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Jackson finds Russell for the layup

videos.description: South Carolina's Tyasha Harris finds Lele Grissett down low for the lay-in.
videos.headline: Harris sets up Grissett on the one-handed dime

videos.description: Tennessee's Anastasia Hayes splits the defense and sinks a layup, earning a trip to the line and a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Hayes hits contested layup in traffic

videos.description: South Carolina's Tyasha Harris finds an opening from downtown and nails a 3-pointer to end the 3rd quarter.
videos.headline: Harris beats the buzzer on 3-pointer

videos.description: South Carolina's Alexis Jennings grabs the one-handed rebound and sinks a contested layup to earn a trip to the line.
videos.headline: Jennings nails contested layup for and-1 opportunity

videos.description: Following a block from Tennessee's Mercedes Russell, Jaime Nared takes it upcourt and converts the tough layup.
videos.headline: Nared extends Tennessee's lead on 3-point play

videos.description: Without star A'ja Wilson who is out with an injured ankle, No. 6 Tennessee makes easy work of No. 9 South Carolina in an 86-70 win.
videos.headline: Tennessee rolls past South Carolina
